A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of a massive glowing vault door embedded in a towering server monolith, its surface covered in intricate circuit patterns that pulse with neon blue and purple light. The vault is partially open, revealing layers of translucent geometric blocks inside arranged like a complex 3D puzzle being rearranged by ethereal robotic arms made of light. The scene is set in a dark industrial space with cables hanging from above and holographic data streams floating around the structure. Rain falls through shafts of light from unseen sources above, creating reflections on the wet metal floor. The mood is mysterious and technical, suggesting the delicate process of accessing and restructuring something precious and protected.
